snippet.title: Naruto Shippuden: The New Era 3D (3DS) Trailer
snippet.description: Nintendo Life - Get into the ninja spirit with this trailer for Naruto Shippuden: The New Area 3D from 505 Games, coming to European 3DS consoles in June. More information at http://www.nintendolife.com
